txt.en: You should gather the supplies scattered around Aragorn's pavilion on the after-battle Pelennor.
Angbor can be found at Aragorn's pavilion on the after-battle Pelennor.\n\nYou should talk to Angbor.
The supply cart can be found at Aragorn's Pavilion.\n\nYou should put the supplies in the crates next to the supply cart.
'Good, good! Now we are one step closer to marching east.'
Angbor has been tasked with preparing for the march eastward and must gather supplies for the journey.

'We are preparing to march soon. We must start packing the supplies that we will need on this journey to the Black Gate. Collect supplies from around the pavilion, then pack them in crates on one of the carts.'
